    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Welcome to Three Alpha One Nine</h2></strong><br><br>3A19 is a challenging, modern approach to platformers and adventure.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3130980/extras/09b5f37ec4ddbfbff1b77c18efa4c1ba.avif?t=1727996855\" width=616 height=332 /></span><br><br>You'll play as 3A19, a specialized robot designed by IMI Energy Solutions to collect Energy Cells located throughout time and space.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >OVERVIEW:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>20 Main levels, each with their own unique locale and soundtrack<br></li><li>20 Hardcore variations of each level with new music, new aesthetics, and significantly harder difficulty.<br></li><li>Hidden &quot;SSD Drives&quot; that reveal hints to 3A19 and IMI's purpose.<br></li><li>Unlockable challenge levels to test your skills INCLUDING a round-based arena.<br></li><li>Numerous enemy types and obstacles<br></li><li>Integrated Sprint, Jump, and Boost system allowing for fast pace, free-flowing motion<br></li><li>Switchable camera system for streamlined play (Normal, Zoomed, and Zoomed Out)<br></li><li>17+ customization unlocks and ranking system to reward speed, precision, and curiosity<br></li><li>Planned FREE content each month including more levels, unlocks, and features </li></ul><br>On your adventure you will encounter various enemies and tricky environments that will test your abilities to the limits. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3130980/extras/d25d1de9be626385d2bb1c54363bf576.avif?t=1727996855\" width=616 height=332 /></span><br><br>Your employer, IMI, will keep you updated on your progress, rank your time and damage limitation skills, as well as reward you for your continued excellence.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3130980/extras/0af77a03ad43dd6e2096302fe2985aba.avif?t=1727996855\" width=616 height=332 /></span><br><br>Be on the lookout for your fallen comrades and their SSD Drives they have left behind. Each one will contain a new insight into IMI's working conditions. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3130980/extras/b27e3019db4fca8f3f0f1bb3da2d4cdb.avif?t=1727996855\" width=616 height=332 /></span><br><br>Every second counts, every jump needs attention, and every cell needs to be collected for the betterment of all humankind. <br><br><strong>Are you up for the test?</strong>",
